======================================================================

python-maigret (Multi-site OSINT username dossier generator)

Maigret collects a dossier on a person by username only, checking for
accounts on a huge number of sites and gathering all the available
information from web pages. No API keys required.

HOME: https://github.com/soxoj/maigret

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-about-time python-aiodns python-aiohttp python-aiohttp-socks python-alive-progress python-arabic-reshaper python-asgiref python-async-timeout python-bidi python-cloudscraper python-colorama python-curl-cffi python-flask python-multidict python-networkx python-platformdirs python-pycountry python-pypdf2 python-pysocks python-pyvis python-reportlab python-requests-futures python-requests-toolbelt python-socid-extractor python-soupsieve python-stem python-torrequest python-typing-extensions python-xhtml2pdf python-xmind python-yarl 

